# SQL Analysis

## Overview
Queried the gym members exercise dataset using SQL to validate and 
expand on findings from the Excel analysis.

## Tools Used
- SQLite Online
- Dataset: Gym Members Exercise Tracking (Kaggle)

## Skills Demonstrated
- SELECT, FROM, WHERE, GROUP BY, ORDER BY
- Aggregate functions: AVG, ROUND
- Aliasing with AS

